description:
• "Best of 2013" at Brazilian App Store!
• Apple Highlighted as "Editors choice!

Kekanto is the best city guide made by real clients that transform their cities. Download FREE now!

Using Kekanto you will be able to: 
•  Find restaurants, bars, hotels, clubs, cafes, etc. near you
• Share reviews of places you visited
• Find the best places in your city
• Follow your friends' reviews and check-ins
• Ask for recommendations to your friends
• Join free and VIP events with Kekanto Community
releaseNotes:
What's new on version 6.4.2:

• Messages: send and receive messages from other users of Kekanto!
• bugfixes and performance improvements.

What's new on version 6.4.2:

• Bookmarks: save and tag your favorite places
• Updates and improvements for iOS 8, including a Notification Center widget
• bugfixes and performance improvements

New on previous versions:
• The places on Kekanto are looking better than ever!
• Friday night and looking for a happy hour bar? Check out our collections and find a perfect place for you!
• New search engine! We are more than ready to explore the city with you
• Filter places and easily view them in a map
